ImageSimplify_Prims

This folder contains a program that implements Prim's Algorithm to create a set of connected components in an image specified by the user. The RGB colours of the components are then averaged to give a simplified image. An example is shown in doc/resources.

Compilation is done through maven. 

Usage: 
mvn package
java -jar target/ImageSimplify_Prims-1.0-jar-with-dependencies.jar input_filename.jpg output_filename.jpg num_components
